WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.543
Good morning I am Simon

00:00:01.696 --> 00:00:03.023
I would like to ask

00:00:03.576 --> 00:00:06.500
How to Reduce Prices and Taxes

00:00:06.501 --> 00:00:07.944
you said my name is Simon

00:00:08.636 --> 00:00:09.276
I already knew

00:00:09.277 --> 00:00:11.564
that there will be a difficult question and a difficult passage

00:00:11.796 --> 00:00:12.596
I give you my word

00:00:12.636 --> 00:00:14.883
that I will set you up for 5 minutes with a man

00:00:15.076 --> 00:00:17.163
who will be the Minister of Finance with us

00:00:17.396 --> 00:00:19.803
tell him directly after your fear
